subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Tennis
Sports Injuries
lead_paragraph: Roger Federer and Serena Williams won in a combined 126 minutes, while Juan Carlos Ferrero edged seventh-seeded Gaël Monfils in a five-set match that stretched nearly five hours.
